44
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:18,480
of the great Primordial personality.

45
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:23,840
The central path of Sushumna of ascendance

46
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:29,120
creates this Primordial Being ultimately, is the final,

47
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:32,880
is the complete form of this ascendance,

48
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:37,600
of the evolution, ends up here.

