00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:07,960
Now, this Primordial Being incarnated on this earth,

57
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:11,080
as I told you that all this aspect incarnates,

58
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:16,760
the central aspect on this earth as Shri Krishna.

59
00:05:18,520 --> 00:05:20,840
