00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:16,520
and She appears to us as a lightning in the sky.

77
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:19,480
She's called as Vishnumaya.

78
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:25,320
All these three centers are very, very important.

79
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,960
When you are collective,

80
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:31,360
then you are ascending through this center.

81
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:33,440
The power is passing through this.

82
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:36,680
Actually the root of this starts from here.

